      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="TheRobin"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="FreeVerse"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="happy"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="nature"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>Except within poetic pale</l>
          <l>I have not found a nightingale,</l> 
          <l>Nor hearkened in a dusky vale</l>
          <l>To song and silence blending;</l>
          <l>No stock-dove have I ever heard,</l>
          <l>Nor listened to a cuckoo-bird,</l>
          <l>Nor seen a lark ascending.</l>
          <l>But I have felt a pulse-beat start</l>
          <l>Because a robin, spending</l>
          <l>The utmost of his simple art</l>
          <l>Some of his pleasure to impart</l>
          <l>While twilight came descending,</l>
          <l>Has found an answer in my heart,</l>
          <l>A sudden comprehending.</l>
                 
